high_descs: Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Grab the Martini glass from the middle of the top shelf, in the refrigerator.
Turn to your right and go to the microwave, above the stove, cross from you.
Place the Martini glass in the microwave, heat it up, then remove it from the microwave.
Turn around and go to the kitchen island to your right.
Place the Martini glass on the left, right corner of the kitchen island.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm Martini glass on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Grab the martini glass from the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the microwave above the stove.
Warm the glass in the microwave for 3 seconds.
Turn around and walk to the green table and face it.
Place the glass on the far left bottom corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a martini glass on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the black fridge ahead.
Open the fridge, pick up the clear martini glass from the top shelf and close the doors.
Turn around and walk to the white stove on the left.
Put the glass inside the microwave above the stove, heat it for a few seconds, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the green table on the left.
Put the heated glass on the far bottom left corner of the green table.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated glass on a table.
